name: Time
description:
This is my first NFT which I dedicate to the Time. I've always been interested in the concept of time and I don't think that I ever understand it at all. This NFT was inspired by all of the time-space theories of time and all films about time travelling that I have ever seen.
I've just frozen some period of time in my NFT which I want to share with you. 
I made it in form of a tarot card and would like to continue this collection.
